1156.text: I'll live up to your expectations!

2033.text: We are well tuned for running and live … This will be a great opportunity to show off our skills to the fullest. All we have to do is win!

2034.text: As a locodol, a Tomakomai Tourism Ambassador, and a fighting Umamusume … I am now invincible!

10000.text: Everyone in Tomakomai is watching over me… I want to be the kind of person who everyone can be proud of.

10001.text: I am sure I will be able to do my best for a long time. Because I fell in love with Tomakomai and met people who support me by my side.

10002.text: It's okay for me to be me. It's okay to be serious and uptight. That's the answer we found together.

10003.text: I keep the New Year's greeting cards of those who have helped me. These connections are really important.

10004.text: Have you had the Haskap Chocolate Cake Igave you yet? I need your honest feedback so we can create a new specialty!

10005.text: After attending pastry classes and making many prototypes, I finally finished it… well, I will be very happy if it suits your palate.

10006.text: I can't tell you how many times I have wished for the best for Tomakomai every time I perform at the Tanabata event… In conclusion, it is only my effort that counts.

10007.text: We used Haskap to make purple candy for Halloween! We want to share the taste of Tomakomai with everyone…!

10008.text: I remember skating as Santa Claus and throwing presents to customers at events in the old days… I miss those days.

10009.text: There is a regular course in Tomakomai to see the lights of the boats. Maybe… someday we can go together.

10010.text: Every year, I have a hard time cleaning up. I have so many gifts, tools for events… I just have so much stuff.

10011.text: Happy Birthday! To repay you for all you've done for me, I'll be your party host today!

10012.text: I made a flower frame out of a Haskap and a Nanakamado. Would you be pleased…?

10013.text: Today is my birthday. Every year, I receive many gifts and good luck charms from my hometown.

10014.text: I'd like to invite you to an event… well, my birthday party. If you don't mind, I'd love to!

10015.text: Oh, there's an announcement! I'll have to check it out… sorry. It was addressed to the trainer, wasn't it?

10016.text: Wow, presents are on their way! I'm so happy to see these things. Let's receive them before we forget!

10017.text: Mission accomplished! Well done! I have to work hard too…!

10018.text: It looks like the event is about to start. This is… a Tomakomai PR opportunity!?

10019.text: It looks like the event is going to be a lot of fun. As a locodol, I can't miss this opportunity…!

10021.text: It looks like the level of Umamusume's directory has been raised. Let's check the results of the trainer's efforts!

20000.text: I'm a little tired, but… no, I'll do my best…!

20001.text: Oh, that's strange… I feel lightheaded , like when I get seasick…

20002.text: My running will make Tomakomai shine…! I'm willing to go through the hardest training!

20003.text: Oh, Tomakomai, the white earth, the paper dancing… ♪ Ha, I feel so good, I can't help it…!

20004.text: I feel like I have a clear "on" switch in side me. I think I'm going to get good results!

20005.text: For our goals, we need a professional plan! Let's me know what we will do this week, Trainer!

20006.text: If you do it, it will be done, if you don't do it, nothing will be done. We must keep moving forward today to achieve our goal!

20007.text: I am in good condition. I've been nourished with Haskap in the morning and Haskap in the afternoon today!

20008.text: I feel kind of distracted today… Oh Ahhhh, focus, focus…!

20009.text: I'm not feeling well… So here we go… work mode! Let's go～………

20010.text: I'm not feeling well… At times like this, I need to recharge my batteries with my own Tomakomai photo album …!

20011.text: It's time for Tomakomai to aim higher and work harder… I'm not good enough, am I…

20021.text: I believe that even if you can cover up for a short period of time with your mental strength, the strain will linger on later. It was the same with my work.

20022.text: …I don't think the results will come if we continue to go through with the show like a mad dash. …I think we should rethink our plan.

20023.text: Thanks to all of you, we are able to greet today in the best possible condition. I will live up to everyone's expectations!

20024.text: In order to etch the name of Tomakomai in everyone's hearts, all we need is a brilliant victory. If it's me now… surely!

20025.text: As a locodol, a Tomakomai Tourism Ambassador, and a fighting Umamusume … I am now invincible!

20026.text: These legs, nurtured in Tomakomai and trained by a trainer, are second to none.

20027.text: Our goal is to get to first place and then to the center! Tomakomai's brilliance is what I want everyone to remember when they return home.

20028.text: We are well tuned for running and live … This will be a great opportunity to show off our skills to the fullest. All we have to do is win!

20029.text: I am sure that everyone in my hometown is watching over me. I will definitely… win!

20030.text: I'm Talmae, a migratory bird from Tomakomai☆… I won't waste the live greetings I've thought up for today!

20031.text: I have been working with my trainer to prepare for victory. I will repay you with a victory.

20032.text: No matter what my condition is, I have to win…! I'll do my best!

20033.text: I will beat back this much adversity. I will overturn even greater adversity in my hometown…!

20034.text: At times like this, everyone in Tomakomai will tell me not to push myself, but… just for today, I'm going to push myself!

20035.text: I am anxious, but… I will not be discouraged. To respond to the people of Tomakomai, I will fight until the very end!

20036.text: The adjustments didn't work out… but I will win. Because my victory is not only for me…!

20037.text: To be honest, I'm not in great shape … but if I can turn things around from here, I'm sure I can make a great appeal…!

20049.text: Thanks to you, I was able to contribute to Tomakomai!

30000.text: Next time… I'm going to win the center!

30001.text: Good enough… but not enough to leave a lasting impression!

30003.text: I can't face everyone back home…!

30004.text: I offer to my hometown, the glory of my victory!

30005.text: Thanks for the support! I'm Tarumae, the star of Tomakomai☆.

30007.text: Thanks for the support! I'm Tarumae, the star of Tomakomai☆.

40001.text: Do you know that town? Tomakomai! Tomakomai is overflowing with deliciousness! So many great places, let's go! Tomakomai!

60000.text: My experience as a locodol… now is the time to put it to use!

60001.text: Tomakomai guys, keep an eye on it!

70001.text: At the time, I was too preoccupied with myself. I thought, "I am going to save Tomakomai…" Now, we are a two-person team.

70010.text: Dressing properly. That's the secret to being cute☆

70014.text: Cute costumes… but the problem is how to promote Tomakomai…

70015.text: Nanakamado, swans, swans… Tomakomai is full of symbols!

70019.text: I love the outfit ☆… hmmm is it a bit pretentious?

71014.text: Cute costumes… but the problem is how to promote Tomakomai…

71015.text: Nanakamado, swans, swans… Tomakomai is full of symbols!

71019.text: I love the outfit ☆… hmmm is it a bit pretentious?

80002.text: The event mission is here♪ Get excited for Christmas! … How about something like that?

90000.text: Good morning! Today, too, I will tell as many people as possible about the beauty of Tomakomai!

90001.text: Like a swan on Lake Utonai! Hokko Tarumae, here we come again today in all our glory♪……………Yes, thank you.

90002.text: Snack time is your chance to promote Haskap! We'll be handing out some great jam-based treats to everyone!

90003.text: Tomakoma～☆…this greeting may not be so bad. What do you think, trainer?

90004.text: I'm going to stick to a simple style… but I still think that dialect is the way to go… oh, sorry! I'm still trying to f igure out the direction of my future activities.

90005.text: Oban-ban-ban☆ I'm Tarumae☆… I wonder if this makes me sound like a locodol or a comedian.

90006.text: It's spring, isn't it? …I might add a cherry blossom-like point to the costume to emphasize the freshness … yes, that might be a good idea.

90007.text: It's hot, and unbearable… and at times like these, the nutritious Haskap! What a surprise! They're in season now!

90008.text: Salmon, hokke, hokki-gai… and so much more. So many things to push one's appetite in the fall, it's hard to keep track!

90009.text: It's that time of year again. I will appeal Tomakomai with my ice dancing skills that I have honed in my hometown!

91000.text: We've asked Ms. Flash to evaluate our prototype haskap sweets. We aim for a taste recognized by the artisans!

91001.text: Falco-san winked at me the moment our eyes met at the concert… I was so thrilled. I was so impressed.

91002.text: The daikon pickles made by Acute are delicious. Next time we have tea, I'll bring some of Tomakomai's famous sweets!

91003.text: When Ricky and I go out to karaoke, we do a lot of choreography. It's just 2 people but it feel like live concert…

91004.text: Actually, I enjoy mountain climbing. I once did PR for a campground near Mt. Tarumae.

91005.text: If I can go in a cute direction for love songs, what direction should I take for rock songs… hmmm… it's a tough one.

91006.text: It's a nice outfit as it is, but if you made the buttons more like shells, for example, it would be even nicer… no?

91007.text: Wearing this dress brings back memories of my early days as a locodol… So many things happened… so many things…

91008.text: The ribbon on the chest is a Japanese water iris. Just like the language of flowers, we hope to bring "happy news" to Tomakomai.

91009.text: It's going to be another tough day. But I'm going to cheer myself up and work hard～☆ …Yeah, I think I did a good job with that one.

91010.text: I am proposing a Tomakomai Fair in the cafeteria. We are currently working on a lunch menu to make it a reality.

91011.text: If you don't look up at the night sky, you won't notice the stars. What Tomakomai needs is for people to first notice their brilliance!

91012.text: I've hosted a hanami event with local characters. You can see some photos if you search for it.

91013.text: I was often invited to other cities during the summer festival season. However, I had to move around by my self… it was quite difficult…

91014.text: I was working more and more on food reports in the fall. I was a little over-zealous in my work, letting my Umamusume's stomach take care of itself …

91015.text: I used to perform at an event in Sapporo and was surprised at the amount of snow. Tomakomai has very little snow.

92000.text: May my success inspire everyone in Tomakomai… and I look forward to working with you today!

92001.text: If I shine, everyone will notice the brilliance of Tomakomai… With this belief, I will do my best!

92002.text: I spent at least 30 minutes stretching , and I kept my heart rate up enough! I can start anytime!

92003.text: You have to learn to be a master…! Just like a hokki-gai clam in season, packed with flavor…!

92005.text: I want to do everything I can for my hometown. Please help us!

92006.text: I am very happy to have met someone who cares about me and Tomakomai. I am truly happy to have met someone who cares about me and Tomakomai.

92007.text: Join forces and make Tomakomai shine. If we make your wish come true… well, why don't the two of you attend a local event?

92011.text: It reminds me of the coast of my hometown… I am getting more and more motivated.

93000.text: We were able to make our precious hometown shine…!

93001.text: I have worked so hard to get this far … thanks to you.

95001.text: I'm sure I'll be able to expand my artistic horizons as a locodol!

95003.text: ホッコータルマエ、はっちゃきこくべ！

95004.text: The fastest locodol, from Tomakomai ～☆… yes that will do!

110000.text: To get closer to our goal, we have to work hard, right?

110001.text: Just like the city of Tomakomai, the school has a long history.

110002.text: Let's get that first place and get some PR!

120000.text: I feel like I've inherited something precious!
